gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 102, Nuggets 100
gameRecap.excerpt: Los Angeles defeats Denver, 102-100. For Los Angeles, Paul George led the way with 28 points, four rebounds, and three steals with James Harden adding 20 points, six rebounds, and eight assists in the victory. Nikola Jokic finished with 36 points, 17 rebounds, and 10 assists with Aaron Gordon recording 18 points, six rebounds, and seven assists for Denver in the losing effort. Los Angeles improves to 48-28, while Denver moves to 53-24 with the loss.
